query:
UPDATE fanbox_posts SET
                    creator_id=?,
                    title=?,
                    body=?,
                    is_body_rich=?,
                    fee=?,
                    published_datetime=datetime(?, 'utc'),
                    updated_datetime=datetime(?, 'utc'),
                    fetched_at=datetime('now', 'utc')
                WHERE id = ?
